name: Version 3.1.5
body: Fix automatic message reload, s.t. new messages are fetched even when the app is closed (especially after a device reboot).

name: Version 3.1.4
body:
- Map filter is persisted across app restarts
- Bugfixes

name: Version 3.1.3
body:
- Made links in user profile descriptions clickable
- Switched the default map style to OpenTopoMap (performance improvement)
- User profiles are now refreshable by swiping them down
- Fixed login issue on devices running Android <=4.4.4
- Bugfixes

name: Version 3.1.0
body:
- Implements the usage of an API key as required by the Warmshowers service.
- Bugfixes.

name: Version 3.0.1
body:
* Fixed issue when login was done with invalid credentials (#321).
* Made the login activity scrollable s.t. the keyboard does not cover e.g. the login button.

name: Version 3.0.0
body:
- FLOSS variant; Google maps are replaced by OpenStreetMap
- Filter for users on the map
- Marker styling for favorite users
- Option to remember the login password
- Data saver mode

name: Version 2.0.3
body:
- Fix navigation not reacting to clicks on some devices.
- Fix several crashes.
- Fix message being sent several times if the first attempt failed.
- Ignore accounts without a userId.
- Message formatting improvemments.
- Add support for multi-line messsage input.

name: Version 2.0.2
body: Fixes crash when entering the wrong login credentials on some devices.

name: Version 2.0.0
body:
This is the new and shiny version of Warmshowers.org for Android. We overhauled the look and feel, fixed so many bugs that we cannot count them - but especially the login issue that many of our users encountered is finally gone!
And last but not least, we introduced messaging into the app. Enjoy!

name: Version 2.0.0-beta2
body: Fixes some crashes of the app.

body:
This is the new and shiny version of Warmshowers.org for Android. We overhauled the look and feel, fixed so many bugs that we cannot count them - but especially the login issue that many of our users encountered is finally gone!

name: Version 1.5.1
body:
Bugs fixed:
* Eventually close the host search progress dialog (#251)
* Move hidden send button in HostContactActivity (#250)

name: Version 1.5.1-beta1
body:
Bugs fixed:
  - Login and operation problems due to missing TLS SNI on older devices (#256).
  - Missing feedback information for users due to API changes (#261).
